						h4 Website Design
						p Transform your vision into a captivating online reality. I specialize in creating visually stunning and intuitive websites that resonate with your audience. From sitemaps and wireframes to high-fidelity mockups, I ensure every detail aligns with your brand identity.
						
			.col-md-4.my-3
				.card.services-content
					= image_tag "homepage/services-landing-pages.jpg", :class=>"card-img", :alt=>"Landing Page Design"
					.card-body
						h4 Landing Page Design
						p Launching a campaign? Let me handcraft a strategic landing page that not only attracts leads but also guides visitors through a seamless customer journey. I focus on creating landing pages that drive engagement and conversions.
			.col-md-4.my-3
				.card.services-content
					= image_tag "homepage/services-other-offerings.jpg", :class=>"card-img", :alt=>"Other Offerings"
					.card-body
						h4 Additional Offerings
						p Gain clarity on your brand vision and attract new customers with creative assets tailored to you and your ideal audience.

		br
		.row
			.col-lg-12
				.text-center
					= link_to "Explore My Services", services_path, :class=>"btn btn-primary mr-3"

